eract with serotonin, muscarinic, benzodiazepine, and beta-adrenergic receptor that would otherwise result in adverse reactions such as dry mouth or sonmolence.  

Onset of action = 0.25 hours; 

Duration of action = 12-24 hours; ', 'DrugBank', 0, 0, 0);
